    "Furthermore, 13% students disagreed that CodeTutor improved their understanding of programming syntax, with a larger proportion of individuals agreeing (33%) or strongly agreeing (25%).",
    "Nearly half of the students (42%) agreed or strongly agreed that CodeTutor helped students build their own understandings, while very few (17%) strongly disagreed or disagreed.",
